      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesnt feel like \"change.\" it just feels empty. like there's nothing left inside to actually grow or fix. how can you fix something that isn't even there? the person i was is gone, and this thing left behind is just... haunting itself. it feels so pointless to keep dragging this around.",
